# ============================================================
# Documentation — `docs/` is tracked (do not blanket-ignore)
# ============================================================
# Previously `docs/` was ignored, so nothing under it was versioned; merges that
# removed docs from a branch could not restore your copies from git. Commit paths
# under docs/public/, docs/internal/, etc. so they survive rebases and merges.
#
# Prompt logs: ignore scratch files, but allow the consolidated append-only log (P5-12).
prompt_history/*
!prompt_history/prompt_history.md

